"\n        title=\"1\"\n        src=\"/static/34a9de3c5b30a12f945fafca0c70d30d/bcf2d/1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/34a9de3c5b30a12f945fafca0c70d30d/d5c4a/1.png 185w,\n/static/34a9de3c5b30a12f945fafca0c70d30d/04e89/1.png 370w,\n/static/34a9de3c5b30a12f945fafca0c70d30d/bcf2d/1.png 740w,\n/static/34a9de3c5b30a12f945fafca0c70d30d/dbb75/1.png 1110w,\n/static/34a9de3c5b30a12f945fafca0c70d30d/a808b/1.png 1480w,\n/static/34a9de3c5b30a12f945fafca0c70d30d/079dc/1.png 3584w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h4 id=\"atom-one-dark-by-mahmoud-ali\"><a href=\"#atom-one-dark-by-mahmoud-ali\" aria-label=\"atom one dark by mahmoud ali permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://github.com/akamud/vscode-theme-onedark\">Atom One Dark</a> by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/akamud\">Mahmoud Ali</a></h4>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 740px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2d50367b7bc7cad78e490bc0683d8f9b/079dc/2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 63.61607142857143%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <i